data.description: This charming ranch-style home, nestled in a tranquil neighborhood in Maple Shade, offers a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The seamless flow between the living room and kitchen creates an ideal space for gatherings and entertaining. Adjacent to the kitchen and living room is a spacious family room, adding to the openness of the layout. It is complete with a charming bar area that offers a perfect spot for relaxation or could be transformed into a personalized retreat. This property is well-suited for individuals looking to downsize or those entering the housing market for the first time. This home is a perfect blank slate, ready for someone to make it their own – a canvas for creating cherished memories and embracing a lifestyle of comfort and enjoyment. Don't miss the chance to put your personal touch on this home – schedule a viewing today and experience its unique charm and versatility! The property is being sold AS-IS. The buyer is responsible for all inspections, including but not limited to certificate of occupancy and fire inspection. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful home yours. Schedule a tour today before it's too late!
